                        <div class="form-text">Public files get a shareable, cacheable URL — <strong>readable</strong> is usually best.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-0">
                        <label class="form-label fw-semibold" for="media-obf-private"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock me-2 text-secondary"></i>Private files</label>
